
Download Mini ISO http://mirror.internode.on.net/pub/ubuntu/ubuntu/dists/xenial/main/installer-amd64/current/images/netboot/mini.iso
Install in VBox
VBoxGuest bridged adapter - advanced promiscuous allow all
2 CPUs
Use all US settings (including mirror)
Hostname "budgie-remix"
Install Security updates automatically
No software selection

